From 7bb8dd0d4014a898ac953e06ab634beb0e0cfd54 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 21:28:29 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Merge Horizon Orchestra features into OpenJarvis
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Brings Orchestra's enterprise and intelligence features into the
OpenJarvis base while preserving all existing UI colors and structure.

UI
  frontend/src/styles/orchestra.css — [data-theme="orchestra"] deep
  blue-violet palette; does not touch existing cyan theme

Billing (from Orchestra)
  billing/stripe.py        — BillingManager, Stripe Meter Events API
  billing/usage_tracker.py — UsageTracker, tier limits, per-customer locks

Briefing scheduler (from Orchestra)
  briefing/briefing_config.py, briefing_monitor.py, briefing_scheduler.py,
  briefing_tools.py, briefing_api.py — daily digest scheduler, APScheduler

Intelligence
  intelligence/hybrid_router.py  — HybridRouter combining Orchestra's
    domain-aware routing with OpenJarvis cost/latency scoring; includes
    brain2/3/4 Nemotron, kimi-k2.5, sonar, gemma-4, claude, grok models
  intelligence/model_council.py  — multi-model parallel deliberation
    adapted from Orchestra; uses HybridRouter; council includes brain2/3/4

Server routes
  server/billing_routes.py  — GET /billing/usage, POST /billing/webhook
  server/briefing_routes.py — GET /briefing/status, POST /briefing/trigger

pyproject.toml
  Added billing and briefing optional dependency groups
